original_title: Eels: Live and in Person! London 2006
overview: Live and In Person! London 2006 is a live album by Eels initially released on their 2008 An Evening with Eels tour as a CD and DVD. The album was later sold through Eels' online store. It documents parts of two performances in London from the Live and In Person! No Strings Attached tour on June 23 and 27 at the Astoria.
title: Eels: Live and in Person! London 2006
